    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="PicGo与github图床搭建"><a href="#PicGo与github图床搭建" class="headerlink" title="PicGo与github图床搭建"></a>PicGo与github图床搭建</h1><p>标签（空格分隔）： 个人博客搭建</p><hr><h2 id="1-首先在github下载PicGo"><a href="#1-首先在github下载PicGo" class="headerlink" title="1.首先在github下载PicGo"></a>1.首先在github下载PicGo</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/Molunerfinn/PicGo">https://github.com/Molunerfinn/PicGo</a><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Romantic-1/ImgBed/main/20250427100543986.png"></p><h2 id="2-github设置仓库存放图片（图床）"><a href="#2-github设置仓库存放图片（图床）" class="headerlink" title="2.github设置仓库存放图片（图床）"></a>2.github设置仓库存放图片（图床）</h2><p>记得选择公开和添加readme文件<br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Romantic-1/ImgBed/main/20250427100729085.png"></p><h2 id="3-PicGo软件下载GitHub-plus上传图片插件"><a href="#3-PicGo软件下载GitHub-plus上传图片插件" class="headerlink" title="3.PicGo软件下载GitHub-plus上传图片插件"></a>3.PicGo软件下载GitHub-plus上传图片插件</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Romantic-1/ImgBed/main/20250427100850971.png"></p><h2 id="3a-在github生成token"><a href="#3a-在github生成token" class="headerlink" title="3a.在github生成token"></a>3a.在github生成token</h2><p>注意需要都选择经典的token<br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Romantic-1/ImgBed/main/20250427101439842.png"></p><h2 id="5-然后配置github-plus的参数配置"><a href="#5-然后配置github-plus的参数配置" class="headerlink" title="5.然后配置github-plus的参数配置"></a>5.然后配置github-plus的参数配置</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Romantic-1/ImgBed/main/20250427101608136.png"></p><h2 id="6-常见问题"><a href="#6-常见问题" class="headerlink" title="6.常见问题"></a>6.常见问题</h2><p>1.上传失败情况1<br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Romantic-1/ImgBed/main/20250427101831218.png"><br>这种情况一般就是开了加速器访问github，关闭加速器即可</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
